<speak version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis" xml:lang="en-IN"><voice name="en-IN-Diya:DragonHDLatestNeural"><p><s>Hey there, <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="diːpti">Deepti</phoneme>. Today, we are going to test one financial idea by following the cash flow rather than memorising the label.</s><break time="350ms"/></p></voice><voice name="en-IN-Arjun:DragonHDLatestNeural"><p><s>Before we accept the structure, what happens if the originator fails and the borrower payments still have to reach investors?</s><break time="350ms"/></p></voice><voice name="en-IN-Diya:DragonHDLatestNeural"><p><s>That is the right question. We must separate legal ownership, collection control, servicing continuity, and the payment priority that determines who receives the cash first.</s></p></voice></speak>